description:
Origin

Valentina was once a homeless orphan who lived on the streets of Moscow in the The Soviet Union until she was adopted by the State. She was raised to be the perfect communist and was eventually recruited alongside Divinity to join an elite team of cosmonauts whose mission was to travel to the end of the universe and investigate it. Upon reaching the universal boundary the group of three cosmonauts came in to contact with an unknown power that fundamentally changed them granting them godlike powers.
